name: Kingman Turquoise Cuff

Vintage sterling silver and Kingman turquoise cuff bracelet.
Kingman Turquoise Mine in Arizona was originally discovered by prehistoric Indians over 1000 years ago - the Turquoise from here is known for its beautiful sky blue color. High-grade Kingman turquoise is a medium to dark blue color and frequently flecked with pyrite and sometimes quartz.
